
ZHENSHUO PRIVACY POLICY
Published on May 20, 2018


WELCOME TO ZHENSHUO SERVICES.

PLEASE READ THIS PRIVACY POLICY CAREFULLY



Welcome to ZhenShuo. This Privacy Policy explains our privacy commitment to our players (hereinafter “Users”). This Privacy Policy is incorporated as part of the ZhenShuo Terms of Use. At ZhenShuo, we collect personal data to support our products and services. According to GDPR, “personal data” means any information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person, directly or indirectly, in particular by reference to an identifier such as a name, an identification number, location data, an online identifier or to one or more factors specific to the physical, physiological, genetic, mental, economic, cultural or social identity of that natural person. By using ZhenShuo’s services, you authorize ZhenShuo to process your personal data according to this Privacy Policy. If you do not accept the terms of this Privacy Policy, please refrain from using our online games or our games’ online functionalities, our websites, our mobile apps and any other online ZhenShuo products and services (hereinafter “Services”).


